   <talk_paragraph index="n1842_shaolong-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Mysterious Tiger Man$<BR>Splendid! Those are some great moves you've got there!<BR>I've finally found a disciple to pass down my One-armed Kung Fu! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-accepting-acceptted" mid="93" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="89"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(The tiger-faced man you saw outside town is staring at you.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1842_shaolong-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1842_shaolong-1-" mid="56" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>I'll tell you more in Prairie Town!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Xiaolong vanishes in a second.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-1-" mid="57" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>This is going to disrupt my schedule...<FONT color=#7e12d2>(He is too engrossed in work that he doesn't notice you.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-a" mid="59" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>You came here faster than I expected. Kakaka! How did you end up in this small town? <BR>You don't even have a pass... You must have never left Lotus Marsh before, have you? </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-b" mid="60" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Tell him what happened in the airship.) </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-c" mid="61" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9571_qu_01.ogg}<BR>I see... So you secretly boarded an airship with fellow villagers to get treatment for your illness but a guy called Suriya and his gang crashed the ship? Krrang... That's unfortunate... By the way, are you sick?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-d" mid="62" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>My arm... (Quietly lift up and show him the mechanic arm.) </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-e" mid="63" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9571_qu_02.ogg}<BR>Aww that's one cool-looking arm! <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Xiaolong reaches out to touch Machina's right arm and black discharge drips from it the moment he touches it.)</FONT> </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-f" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Don't touch! It's dangerous! This arm is... Argh...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-g" mid="65" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9571_qu_03.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(At the place where the black liquid dripped, grass turned brown and holes were made in clothes and leather. But surprisingly, nothing happened to Xiaolong's hand that touched it.)</FONT> <BR>Hey... What's wrong with your arm?! You look pale! What happened?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-h" mid="66" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That's what I need treatment for... My arm has been replaced with a prosthetic one but black discharge keeps oozing out from the part where my arm was cut. Usually anything that comes into contact with it would corrode but your hand is fine... Why is that?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-i" mid="68" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9571_qu_04.ogg}<BR>Hahaha! That's because I'm a master of One-armed Kung Fu!<BR>You get to enjoy eternal life when you master this kung fu.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-j" mid="69" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9571_qu_05.ogg}<BR>Do you want to learn this kung fu that can give you life?<BR>There could be side effects but maybe you won't have them. So how does that sound? You have nothing to lose to stop the ooze! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-k" mid="70" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>He seems like a conman…</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-l" mid="71" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9571_qu_06.ogg}<BR>What are you mumbling?! <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Xiaolong turns serious.)</FONT> <BR>To tell you the truth, I... used to be a human! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-m" mid="72" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9571_qu_07.ogg}<BR>Well, you know what the side effects are now. But I'm okay with it. Others turned into praying mantis or tadpoles! I'm lucky to have turned into a terrific tiger. By the way, this is a secret but... I may look young but I'm more than 300 years old! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-n" mid="73" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I shouldn't talk to this swindler anymore.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-o" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_9571_qu_08.ogg}<BR>You don't believe me? But what have you got to lose? Try learning the One-armed Kung Fu from me. I wonder what will happen when your disease is combined with my kung fu.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-p" mid="75" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Well then….</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-q" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Great! Call me master from today onwards! You can check the various skills of the One-armed Kung Fu when you press the <FONT color=#387206>[K]</FONT> key. <BR>Learn them one by one.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-r" mid="77" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>I'll teach you how to evade too. Double tap the direction key or press <FONT color=#387206> [ Shift ]</FONT> together with the direction key to evade the attacks! Evading is the most fundamental skill of any kung fu. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-1-s" mid="78" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I know such things already... Whatever, I'll call you master for now. Argh...! I really hope this kung fu will relieve the pain.<BR>And I need to find my fellow villagers. We need to go to the Red Merchants and get cured before it's too late.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-1-s" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-2" mid="79" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>The Red Merchants?! Krrang! They are an infamous lot...<BR>Why don't you ask Blacksmith Dorin about the airship you were on? I heard he was supposed to get supplies from an airship that was supposed to pass by this town today.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1841_shaolong-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_shaolong.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1841_shaolong-2-" mid="81" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Dorin owes me a lot so he'll be nice to you even though you are a hybrid. <BR>Be careful not to get spotted by the mayor or the guards on your way to Dorin! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-2-a" mid="82" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>Hmm??? I've never seen you around before... Are you allowed to stay in this town? </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-2-b" mid="83" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Xiaolong told me to come here. </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-2-c" mid="84" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>Xiaolong? Oh that talkative tiger? Why would he want you to come and see me? <BR>I'm not really keen on trading with the hybrids... </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-2-d" mid="85" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Do you know anything about the airship that was supposed to pass by this village today? </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-2-e" mid="96" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-2-!next" mid="87" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Dorin angrily bangs the table with the hammer he was holding.)</FONT> <BR>The airship?! Of course I know! Now I can't make my order in time because that damn ship crashed!</html>]]></talk_question>
